ji\" />"},{"pid":"15e2186f488a82dee4d84b18311b40801cae563e","tid":759420,"uid":37431,"like":22,"dislike":6,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T15:29:43.000Z","msg":"搭巴士，坐你前面個廢老咳唔遮住個口，擘大佢個口用界刀割佢斷條脷，一唔割一路問佢「識唔識遮口呀，知唔知自己做錯咩呀？」<br />\n佢流晒眼淚求你放過佢，你唔肯，最後要佢自己食返條脷吞落肚<br />\n<br />\n（純幻想，現實唔會做）"},{"pid":"0dd86e7999597e5044fb062233e0e9e64d502380","tid":759420,"uid":37431,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"15e2186f488a82dee4d84b18311b40801cae563e","tid":759420,"uid":37431,"like":22,"dislike":6,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T15:29:43.000Z","msg":"搭巴士，坐你前面個廢老咳唔遮住個口，擘大佢個口用界刀割佢斷條脷，一唔割一路問佢「識唔識遮口呀，知唔知自己做錯咩呀？」<br />\n佢流晒眼淚求你放過佢，你唔肯，最後要佢自己食返條脷吞落肚<br />\n<br />\n（純幻想，現實唔會做）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T15:31:23.000Z","msg":"但真心好想拍呢個系列嘅電影，日常生活中冇品嘅人接受極殘酷嘅懲罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a2eb93e59d67182ebeffd1400e41c61764f621","tid":759420,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T07:56:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫推"},{"pid":"a7687b3e7f1a39f457a494f6099f54cf6ab022b1","tid":759420,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:09:44.000Z","msg":"留名等睇樓主作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"decb173d0886755a89c71c2296f22847d3e0f8a2","tid":759420,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T10:58:24.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪畫緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aaca69b487751b36b2456c8268709f39913f3f8","tid":759420,"uid":138632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"decb173d0886755a89c71c2296f22847d3e0f8a2","tid":759420,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T10:58:24.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪畫緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T14:42:49.000Z","msg":"俾啲時間<img src=\"/assets/fa