Time":"2018-07-30T07:21:43.000Z","msg":"我只係覺得巴打個idea幾有趣但樓主一句唔畫咁達埋去有啲可惜姐 惡撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f35c96a6bba9539529e5919d61b2b9bebcbe82a","tid":759420,"uid":138632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:31:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/135849_49462b7dc37a2d2b5de6d3843d4c8c75.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F135849_49462b7dc37a2d2b5de6d3843d4c8c75.png&h=f42804a1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n要自己諗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8182a3087e7ed439144da7e2e7bac27c5bead67","tid":759420,"uid":25902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T08:01:59.000Z","msg":"鏡頭分別對住兩個人<br />\n青年挨坐響床邊 手肘放響窗邊 托住頭 悲傷咁望住出面落緊雨既天<br />\n<br />\n一個係著住婚紗 拎住花球 響婚紗店對住塊鏡試緊婚紗既少女 表情苦笑<br />\n不遠處仲有一個臉容模糊 西裝骨骨既男士 插住袋笑住咁望住鏡入面既女仔<br />\n<br />\n冇人知道兩個人發生既事 只需要知道兩個人已經由兩條交錯既線 變為平行線"},{"pid":"1fb8d83856b0bb1f086747749ac2cb5d0b2d9a17","tid":759420,"uid":37431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dd86e7999597e5044fb062233e0e9e64d502380","tid":759420,"uid":37431,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"15e2186f488a82dee4d84b18311b40801cae563e","tid":759420,"uid":37431,"like":22,"dislike":6,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T15:29:43.000Z","msg":"搭巴士，坐你前面個廢老咳唔遮住個口，擘大佢個口用界刀割佢斷條脷，一唔割一路問佢「識唔識遮口呀，知唔知自己做錯咩呀？」<br />\n佢流晒眼淚求你放過佢，你唔肯，最後要佢自己食返條脷吞落肚<br />\n<br />\n（純幻想，現實唔會做）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T15:31:23.000Z","msg":"但真心好想拍呢個系列嘅電影，日常生活中冇品嘅人接受極殘酷嘅懲罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:04:25.000Z","msg":"我咪自己諗左囉, 你又唔畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除左廢老咳唔遮口呢個scene<br />\n<br />\n仲有廢老衝閘被裝上刀片的閘口割開兩半<br />\n<br />\n仲有地盤佬做火車頭比人綁起佢用煙頭辣佢龜頭"},{"pid":"b64f47bf782c61f4c031c7adef5e370fd092ef73","tid":759420,"uid":35136,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:27:23.000Z","msg":"有一晚 係雪地上嘅一間小屋<br />\n個窗結晒冰<br />\n一個少女放咗盞煤氣燈係窗邊張臺<br />\n燈嘅熱力熔咗窗上面啲冰 <br />\n熔咗一個圓 見到個少女向外望"},{"pid":"d03c1ec576a0800ac6d5c0994823dc1347081d14","tid":759420,"uid":138632,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:29:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由城市走去森林</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12107a970dab8221303695a6d21f3c1c7f41b649","tid":759420,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:40:53.000Z","msg":"係青馬大橋最高處府視香港夜景"},{"pid":"a6c636d737b4610e313adc84dff96aa0431f5021","tid":759420,"uid":126466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:41:39.000Z","msg":"天空由藍變黑"},{"pid":"75ac94498fd7c08ad228d69a03a93fb9368cd6fa","tid":759420,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:46:22.000Z","msg":"武將在泰山山頂 望落有雲海既山腳<br />\n大地在我腳下既氣勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9a3818efbbb220ce1683b6b17df30f975c39c0","tid":759420,"uid":191296,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T16:11:53.000Z","msg":"男同學坐前面，女同學坐後面<br />\n男同學另轉&quot;伏&quot;喺女同學張枱<br />\n兩個人互望"}]}